title: Butter chicken
description: Butter Chicken is creamy and easy to make right at home in one pan with simple ingredients! Full of incredible flavours, it rivals any Indian restaurant! Aromatic golden chicken pieces in an incredible creamy curry sauce, this Butter Chicken recipe is one of the best you will try!
amount: 6 people
preb time: 15 min 
cook time: 30 min
total time: 45 min
calories: 580 

ingredients:    
    boneless chicken (28 oz)  
    plain yogurt (0.5 cup)    
    minced garlic (0.5 tbsp)  
    garam masala (2 tsp)
    turmeric (1 tsp)
    ground cumin (1 tsp)
    red chili powder (1 tsp)
    salt (1 tsp)

    oilve oil (2 tbsp)
    ghee (2 tbsp)
    chopped onion (1)
    minced garlic (0.5 tbsp)
    minced ginger (1 tbsp)
    ground cumin (0.5 tsp)
    garam masala (0.5 tsp)
    ground coriander (1 tsp)
    crushed tomatoes (14 oz)
    red chili powder (1 tsp)
    salt (0.25 tsp)  \\\ (1/4 tsp)
    heavy cream (1 cup)
    sugar (1 tbsp)
    kasoori methi (0.5 tsp)

kitchenware:
    bowl
    skillet
    blender
procedure:

    with(boneless chicken, plain yogurt, minced garlic(0.5 cup), garam masala(2 tsp), turmeric(1 tsp), ground cumin(1 tsp), red chili powder(half), salt(1 tsp)) using(bowl):
        On the night before combine the chicken pieces in a [bowl] with all of the ingredients for the chiken marinade: 0.5 cup of [minced garlic], 2 tsp [garam masala], 1 tsp [turmeric], 1 tsp [ground cumin],1 tsp [red chili powder] and 1 tsp [salt].

        yield: marrinated chicken

    with(olive oil, marrinated chicken) using(skillet):
        Heat the [olive oil] in a large [skillet] When sizzling add the [marrinated chicken] in batches of 2 or 3 to aboid overcrowding the pan.
        Fry until browned with 3 minutes on each side. Take it off the [skillet] and put it aside for now.

        yield: fried chicken

    with(ghee, chopped onion) using(skillet):
        Heat [ghee] in the same [skillet:olive oil]. Fry the [chopped onions:chopped onion] for about 6 minutes, scrape off any browned bits stuck on the bottom of the pan. 

        yield:
            buttered onions   

    with(buttered onions,minced garlic(0.5 tbsp), minced ginger, ground coriander, garam masala (0.5 tsp)) using(skillet):
        Add 0.5 tbsp [minced garlic] and 1 tbsp of [minced ginger] to [skillet:] and saute for 1 minute, then add the ground coriander and 0.5 tsp of garam masala.
        Cook for about 20 seconds until fragrant, while stirring occasionally.
        yield:
            sauce mix

    with(sauce mix, crushed tomatoes, red chili powder(half), salt(0.25 tbsp)) using(skillet):
        Add {crushed tomatoes}, 1 tsp of [red chili powder] and 0.25 tbsp of [salt]. Let simmer for about 10-15 minutes, stirring occasionally until sauce thickens and becomes a deep brown red colour.
        update:
            sauce mix

    with(sauce mix) using(blender):
        remove [skillet:sauce mix] from the heat, scoop mixture into a [blender] and blend until smooth.

        update:
            sauce mix
   
    with(sauce mix, heavy cream, sugar, kasoori methi, fried chicken) using(skillet):
        Pour the pur√©ed [sauce mix] back into the [skillet]. Stir the [heavy cream], [sugar] and crushed [kasoori methi] through the [sauce mix]. 
        Add the [fried chicken] with juices back into the [skillet:sauce mix] and cook for an additional 8-10 minutes until [fried chicken] is cooked through and the [sauce mix] is thick and bubbling.

        yield:
            Butter chicken

    done(Butter chicken)

